WEBVTT

00:11.670 --> 00:12.670
For the first medicine,

00:12.490 --> 00:15.330
[2015] [Department of Psychiatry]

00:12.880 --> 00:14.960
half a pill a day keeps your mood stable.

00:14.960 --> 00:16.190
Within half an hour to an hour,

00:16.190 --> 00:17.650
you'll fall right asleep.

00:18.320 --> 00:19.550
It'll affect my work.

00:20.670 --> 00:21.670
Professor Jiang,

00:21.920 --> 00:24.390
you can stop thinking
about your work for now.

00:24.390 --> 00:26.450
Clear your mind, calm your emotions,

00:26.710 --> 00:28.670
and ease your nerves.

00:28.670 --> 00:29.230
Okay?

00:30.840 --> 00:32.840
Well, there is another option,

00:32.870 --> 00:34.390
the one we talked about last time.

00:34.390 --> 00:36.720
This medicine can be taken continuously.

00:36.790 --> 00:38.850
Take two pills for the first two days,

00:38.910 --> 00:40.230
then we'll see.

00:40.260 --> 00:41.790
If the situation improves,

00:42.150 --> 00:43.240
we can reduce the dosage appropriately.

00:43.240 --> 00:45.240
But many of my patients have reported

00:45.240 --> 00:47.560
that this medicine
has certain side effects.

00:47.560 --> 00:49.220
It'll affect my mental agility...

00:49.220 --> 00:49.990
I told you.

00:50.280 --> 00:52.010
Stop thinking about your work.

00:56.480 --> 00:58.010
It'll give you nightmares.

01:01.110 --> 01:02.280
I'll take this one.

01:03.420 --> 01:04.560
Your current condition

01:04.560 --> 01:06.230
is very serious.

01:07.000 --> 01:10.130
Let's first take the one
that can stabilize you quickly.

01:11.220 --> 01:12.560
I'll prescribe it for you.

01:12.560 --> 01:14.000
Take it when you need to.

01:14.200 --> 01:16.000
Don't skip it just because

01:16.200 --> 01:17.400
you're afraid
that it might affect your thinking

01:17.400 --> 01:18.560
or slow you down.

01:19.360 --> 01:21.140
I've seen many people like you.

01:21.760 --> 01:22.840
I'll say it again.

01:23.400 --> 01:24.430
Pushing your brain too hard

01:24.430 --> 01:27.000
takes a heavy toll on you.

01:28.150 --> 01:29.120
Professor Jiang,

01:29.120 --> 01:31.400
staying healthy and staying alive

01:31.710 --> 01:33.910
are much more important than your work.

01:34.280 --> 01:34.840
Okay.

02:54.329 --> 03:00.030
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:00.360 --> 03:02.780
[Episode 8]

03:19.270 --> 03:22.840
[Team Furis VS Team Jiabotubo]

03:28.829 --> 03:31.130
[Wangtu Scrap Yard]

03:43.770 --> 03:44.310
Police!

03:44.430 --> 03:44.890
Freeze!

03:44.890 --> 03:45.350
Freeze!

03:47.079 --> 03:47.680
Don't move!

03:47.680 --> 03:48.150
Police!

03:48.520 --> 03:49.180
Don't move!

03:49.470 --> 03:49.870
Freeze!

03:49.870 --> 03:50.870
Police! Stop!

03:51.150 --> 03:52.280
Police!

03:54.760 --> 03:55.329
Don't run!

03:55.329 --> 03:55.790
Freeze!

03:56.520 --> 03:57.120
Don't run!

03:59.070 --> 03:59.790
Here! Right here!

03:59.790 --> 04:00.650
Take them away!

04:09.910 --> 04:10.570
Reporting.

04:10.670 --> 04:12.000
Mission accomplished.

04:15.060 --> 04:15.840
Cheng.

04:16.560 --> 04:17.620
What are you doing?

04:18.350 --> 04:19.680
Having... having a late-night snack.

04:19.680 --> 04:20.490
I told you to stay on lookout.

04:20.490 --> 04:21.829
Why are you having snack?

04:21.829 --> 04:22.430
No, Cheng.

04:22.480 --> 04:24.600
We happened to pass by
a famous barbecue place.

04:24.600 --> 04:25.360
It tastes good.

04:25.360 --> 04:27.090
We figured we'd bring you some.

04:27.450 --> 04:28.580
Come back when you're finished.

04:28.580 --> 04:29.380
Stop tailing.

04:29.750 --> 04:30.720
No, Cheng.

04:30.950 --> 04:31.840
We know we were wrong.

04:31.840 --> 04:32.800
We'll go back to tailing

04:32.800 --> 04:34.060
right after we finish.

04:34.860 --> 04:36.210
I told you to stop tailing.

04:36.210 --> 04:37.740
That place has been busted.

04:38.870 --> 04:39.390
Wait.

04:39.600 --> 04:40.400
Did we do it?

04:41.170 --> 04:42.700
What are you talking about?

04:42.710 --> 04:43.850
We don't have the ability to do that,

04:43.850 --> 04:44.460
okay?

04:55.040 --> 04:55.830
Remember.

04:57.360 --> 04:58.340
Don't give your opponent

04:58.340 --> 05:00.310
any chance to succeed.

05:02.900 --> 05:05.700
Pin them to the ground
and wipe the floor with them.

05:07.060 --> 05:08.380
At the end of the day,

05:09.750 --> 05:11.810
you police are the ones I can count on.

05:12.440 --> 05:15.390
Boss, that doesn't
sound like a compliment.

05:19.950 --> 05:20.690
But boss,

05:21.660 --> 05:24.590
now that Old Scorpion's new channel
has been busted,

05:24.890 --> 05:26.650
will he really go back to us?

05:29.000 --> 05:31.000
We've been in this for so many years.

05:31.350 --> 05:33.300
He can't just toss us aside.

05:34.890 --> 05:35.810
Let me tell you.

05:36.600 --> 05:39.120
If the goods get stuck in their own hands,

05:40.470 --> 05:41.909
they would suffer too.

05:43.510 --> 05:44.430
Tell me,

05:44.830 --> 05:45.960
what's on your mind?

05:47.680 --> 05:49.270
First, let them get anxious.

05:49.270 --> 05:50.270
Then,

05:51.270 --> 05:53.390
we offer them some new plans.

05:53.980 --> 05:56.980
We give them what they want
and provide what they need.

06:00.310 --> 06:00.920
Boss,

06:02.130 --> 06:03.930
I heard from Qiu Ye

06:03.960 --> 06:05.090
that Old Scorpion

06:05.610 --> 06:07.140
lost a very important young man

06:07.140 --> 06:09.000
under his command five years ago.

06:11.430 --> 06:12.070
So?

06:13.140 --> 06:15.410
That means Old Scorpion values talent.

06:15.970 --> 06:17.170
So?

06:18.560 --> 06:20.120
I'm a young man.

06:22.920 --> 06:23.720
Cheng,

06:24.440 --> 06:26.170
you've got quite the ambition.

06:32.370 --> 06:34.370
Boss, I'll still say the same thing.

06:34.780 --> 06:36.130
You brought me into this business.

06:36.130 --> 06:37.460
So no matter how far I go,

06:37.480 --> 06:39.480
I'll only answer to the He brothers.

06:39.800 --> 06:41.040
But what I can't stomach now

06:41.040 --> 06:42.580
is that Lai San has taken all the meat

06:42.580 --> 06:43.480
and left me with just the bone.

06:43.480 --> 06:44.810
That's not right, is it?

06:45.310 --> 06:46.480
Now that things are tense,

06:46.480 --> 06:47.310
the market is bad,

06:47.310 --> 06:48.860
and Old Scorpion still has that attitude,

06:48.860 --> 06:50.659
I have to figure out a way myself.

06:51.940 --> 06:54.270
Since there's someone in his inner circle

06:54.620 --> 06:56.480
who is willing to show me the ropes,

06:56.480 --> 06:58.390
whatever Lai San cost you,

06:58.480 --> 06:59.610
I'll make it all back

06:59.630 --> 07:00.690
for you.

07:05.000 --> 07:06.460
It just depends on whether

07:06.680 --> 07:08.540
you are willing to bet on me, boss.

07:13.190 --> 07:14.600
Don't tell me

07:15.630 --> 07:17.290
you haven't slept with Qiu Ye.

07:19.040 --> 07:20.470
I'm taking a break.

07:22.900 --> 07:23.820
Maybe later.

07:32.840 --> 07:35.450
[Tomb of the Martyr, Zhou Chuan]

07:37.630 --> 07:39.630
I'll leave you two alone for a while.

07:57.659 --> 07:58.250
Chuan.

08:02.340 --> 08:03.050
I'm here.

08:04.740 --> 08:06.600
The weather is really nice today.

08:06.860 --> 08:08.860
Let's enjoy the sunshine together.

08:11.370 --> 08:12.280
We had a lead

08:12.620 --> 08:13.280
on the case,

08:15.110 --> 08:16.370
but it went cold again.

08:16.500 --> 08:17.820
But don't worry.

08:18.650 --> 08:20.650
I'll definitely keep following it.

08:21.580 --> 08:22.390
Two days ago,

08:22.460 --> 08:24.590
Wei told me there was new information.

08:25.270 --> 08:26.330
I'll keep looking.

08:27.750 --> 08:30.010
I'll definitely figure everything out.

08:32.870 --> 08:33.630
By the way,

08:33.909 --> 08:34.789
yesterday,

08:35.419 --> 08:36.700
I saw Wei and Bin.

08:38.179 --> 08:39.150
Especially Bin,

08:39.230 --> 08:40.470
he has really made something of himself.

08:40.470 --> 08:41.870
He even opened a restaurant.

08:41.870 --> 08:43.200
It's pretty delicious.

08:43.820 --> 08:45.080
Wei is also doing well.

08:45.510 --> 08:47.780
He successfully joined
the Provincial Bureau.

08:47.780 --> 08:49.910
And he's going to be a father this fall.

08:53.390 --> 08:54.590
Time flies

08:55.420 --> 08:56.700
so fast.

08:57.990 --> 08:59.520
I still remember last year,

08:59.870 --> 09:00.990
he sighed to me,

09:03.660 --> 09:05.990
saying that back when you were still here,

09:06.750 --> 09:08.610
they all saw you as the role model.

09:09.350 --> 09:11.550
They wanted to match you in everything.

09:13.110 --> 09:14.420
Training,

09:15.590 --> 09:16.900
work,

09:18.060 --> 09:19.320
even their love lives.

09:20.110 --> 09:21.770
They all wanted to be like you.

09:25.510 --> 09:26.590
Me too.

09:27.270 --> 09:27.900
Chuan,

09:32.510 --> 09:34.370
you've always been my role model.

09:41.400 --> 09:42.040
Chuan,

09:43.120 --> 09:44.480
I miss you.

09:45.870 --> 09:47.120
If only

09:49.980 --> 09:51.110
you were still here.

09:57.100 --> 09:58.010
Enough of that.

10:08.860 --> 10:10.650
Take a look over there.

10:12.150 --> 10:13.260
See that guy?

10:14.040 --> 10:15.570
He's standing right there.

10:17.530 --> 10:18.690
I married him.

10:21.270 --> 10:22.200
Jiang Hansheng.

10:25.390 --> 10:26.850
Do you still remember him?

10:28.840 --> 10:30.560
He used to live next door to us.

10:33.270 --> 10:34.670
He treats me really well.

10:36.110 --> 10:37.040
Mom and Dad

10:37.630 --> 10:38.870
both like him a lot.

10:41.270 --> 10:41.920
Chuan,

10:43.350 --> 10:44.950
you can rest easy now, right?

10:45.470 --> 10:46.600
I'm doing very well.

11:01.030 --> 11:02.100
Am I interrupting?

11:03.860 --> 11:04.740
No.

11:04.770 --> 11:07.030
I was just introducing you to my brother.

11:07.610 --> 11:08.540
Is he satisfied?

11:10.000 --> 11:11.200
He is very satisfied.

11:11.840 --> 11:12.570
That's good.

11:13.200 --> 11:13.800
Let's go.

11:16.950 --> 11:18.480
I have something to say too.

11:18.880 --> 11:19.400
Okay.

11:19.920 --> 11:21.400
I'll go start the car then.

11:39.820 --> 11:40.340
Chuan,

11:41.830 --> 11:43.160
I'm visiting you again.

11:44.050 --> 11:46.660
This is the first time
Zhou Jin and I came to see you together.

11:46.660 --> 11:47.920
We are both doing well.

11:48.890 --> 11:50.550
Mom and Dad are doing well too.

11:52.240 --> 11:53.050
Don't worry,

11:54.470 --> 11:56.870
I'll definitely
take good care of Zhou Jin.

12:32.930 --> 12:33.650
Zhou Jin.

12:38.200 --> 12:38.930
Zhou Jin!

12:47.430 --> 12:48.030
Hansheng!

12:48.080 --> 12:48.880
What's wrong?

12:49.400 --> 12:50.330
Jiang Hansheng.

12:50.640 --> 12:51.900
What's wrong with you?

12:52.280 --> 12:52.880
I'm sorry.

12:53.000 --> 12:54.250
Sorry for what?

12:54.470 --> 12:56.270
Okay. The day before yesterday,

12:56.290 --> 12:57.500
I thought I crossed the line

12:57.500 --> 12:58.700
and it was my problem!

12:58.830 --> 12:59.620
But today,

13:00.210 --> 13:00.930
we're even!

13:01.640 --> 13:02.310
Bin.

13:03.160 --> 13:03.830
Bin!

13:37.670 --> 13:38.600
Jiang Hansheng,

13:38.880 --> 13:40.140
I need an explanation.

13:42.710 --> 13:44.440
I mistook him for someone else.

13:45.190 --> 13:46.720
Who did you mistake him for?

14:10.190 --> 14:11.050
Anti-anxiety?

14:12.000 --> 14:13.330
Why are you taking this?

14:13.390 --> 14:15.520
And why do you always
keep it in the car?

14:18.040 --> 14:19.100
I'm not a criminal.

14:19.710 --> 14:20.950
I never said you were.

14:22.040 --> 14:23.970
But I don't want someone close to me

14:24.550 --> 14:25.400
to lie to me.

14:26.790 --> 14:29.390
I won't ask about things
you don't want to tell.

14:29.430 --> 14:30.430
But I want to know,

14:30.920 --> 14:32.670
when you pushed Yan Bin just now,

14:32.670 --> 14:34.470
what exactly were you thinking?

14:34.830 --> 14:35.690
To protect you.

14:42.430 --> 14:43.430
So,

14:46.160 --> 14:46.950
you mistook him

14:46.950 --> 14:47.950
for someone else.

14:48.880 --> 14:50.610
You think someone will hurt me.

14:52.000 --> 14:53.060
Who is that person?

15:09.920 --> 15:10.470
Zhou Jin.

15:14.160 --> 15:16.490
I used to carry out some special missions.

15:16.830 --> 15:17.960
They left me on edge.

15:20.000 --> 15:21.520
You weren't just some researcher

15:21.520 --> 15:23.470
back at the Provincial Bureau, right?

15:23.470 --> 15:24.280
Otherwise, they wouldn't have let you

15:24.280 --> 15:25.880
carry out special missions.

15:26.520 --> 15:28.580
You've worked on the front lines too.

15:33.830 --> 15:35.160
What exactly were they?

15:35.920 --> 15:36.780
What missions?

15:39.190 --> 15:40.120
Are there rules?

15:40.760 --> 15:41.760
So you can't tell?

15:55.920 --> 15:56.470
Zhou Jin,

15:57.160 --> 15:58.090
I won't hurt you,

15:58.710 --> 16:00.570
and I won't hurt innocent people.

16:00.830 --> 16:01.760
Don't be afraid,

16:02.310 --> 16:02.920
okay?

16:07.640 --> 16:08.840
Why would I be afraid?

16:13.000 --> 16:14.920
It's just that I don't know you
well enough,

16:14.920 --> 16:15.850
Jiang Hansheng.

16:17.120 --> 16:18.520
I only found out recently

16:18.670 --> 16:20.710
that you used to work
at the Provincial Bureau.

16:20.710 --> 16:22.570
There are many major cases there.

16:23.590 --> 16:25.830
Front-line work, no matter where you are,

16:25.830 --> 16:27.030
is always dangerous.

16:28.670 --> 16:29.240
I get it.

16:36.530 --> 16:38.530
They're just your stress responses

16:38.710 --> 16:39.780
and muscle memory.

16:41.590 --> 16:42.470
I understand.

16:45.640 --> 16:46.170
However,

16:47.880 --> 16:49.240
I'm not an ordinary person.

16:49.240 --> 16:50.300
I'm a policewoman.

16:51.000 --> 16:52.190
Don't do that again,

16:52.880 --> 16:53.280
okay?

16:55.350 --> 16:56.350
As for criminals,

16:58.000 --> 16:59.730
if they dare to lay a hand on you,

17:00.280 --> 17:02.140
I'll show them what the runner-up

17:03.640 --> 17:05.119
of the police academy combat competition

17:05.119 --> 17:06.089
is capable of.

17:12.119 --> 17:12.710
Zhou Jin.

17:14.839 --> 17:17.640
This is the first time
you've hugged me on your own.

17:19.560 --> 17:20.160
Is it?

17:25.470 --> 17:26.069
Thank you.

17:57.810 --> 18:01.200
[Zhao Xiaoyu]
[Resident of Lishui Residential Area]

18:08.270 --> 18:09.000
Are you okay?

18:11.910 --> 18:13.430
I'm fine. Thanks.

18:25.210 --> 18:26.270
You drank too much.

18:27.670 --> 18:29.600
It's dangerous to stay here alone.

18:30.400 --> 18:31.330
I want to go home.

18:33.120 --> 18:34.250
Are you in a bad mood?

18:42.840 --> 18:44.300
Is your home far from here?

18:45.190 --> 18:45.750
Yes.

18:54.030 --> 18:55.070
Your clothes

18:58.030 --> 18:59.090
feel comfortable.

19:09.560 --> 19:10.920
Let me take you home.

19:22.710 --> 19:23.240
Let's go.

19:27.130 --> 19:27.810
Slow down.

19:32.030 --> 19:33.320
Your red dress

19:35.360 --> 19:37.090
seems to be missing something.

19:52.770 --> 19:53.660
Door unlocked.

19:53.680 --> 19:54.870
Welcome home.

20:00.510 --> 20:01.190
Sir.

20:01.430 --> 20:03.630
All this time off has made you lazy, huh?

20:04.880 --> 20:06.920
No, I'm ready to get back to work anytime.

20:06.220 --> 20:07.670
[Wang Pengze]

20:08.230 --> 20:08.880
Listen,

20:09.870 --> 20:11.630
the final results

20:12.160 --> 20:13.920
for your misconduct

20:14.190 --> 20:16.120
during the interrogation are out.

20:16.400 --> 20:18.460
You're getting a unit-wide warning.

20:18.470 --> 20:19.800
The suspension is over,

20:20.220 --> 20:22.640
but you've got a public self-criticism
at the end of the month.

20:22.640 --> 20:23.320
Really?

20:23.410 --> 20:24.920
You sound pretty happy about it.

20:24.920 --> 20:27.120
Of course. That means I'm back on the job.

20:27.120 --> 20:27.840
Report back

20:28.030 --> 20:28.880
this afternoon.

20:28.880 --> 20:29.410
Yes, sir.

20:32.320 --> 20:33.950
Is Professor Jiang with you?

20:33.990 --> 20:35.190
Yes. What is it?

20:35.190 --> 20:36.320
Put him on the phone.

20:36.850 --> 20:37.430
Okay.

20:38.510 --> 20:39.710
My mentor, Chief Tan.

20:43.080 --> 20:43.880
Chief Tan.

20:44.080 --> 20:45.410
This is Jiang Hansheng.

20:48.400 --> 20:49.560
You little pup.

20:49.880 --> 20:51.280
You've grown some wings.

20:51.590 --> 20:53.190
How dare you ignore my calls!

20:54.200 --> 20:54.790
Sir.

20:55.190 --> 20:56.920
Now you remember to call me Sir!

20:58.120 --> 20:59.120
Why are you there?

20:59.320 --> 21:00.400
Something happened.

21:00.400 --> 21:01.860
I'll tell you when we meet.

21:02.070 --> 21:02.680
Bring

21:03.130 --> 21:03.950
that little girl, Zhou,

21:03.950 --> 21:04.560
with you.

21:06.030 --> 21:06.510
Okay.

21:12.800 --> 21:13.800
Here.

21:15.030 --> 21:15.840
Sir.

21:16.400 --> 21:17.260
Director Wang?

21:18.540 --> 21:19.470
He's in Haizhou.

21:19.710 --> 21:20.770
He wants to see you.

21:20.950 --> 21:21.800
See me?

21:22.880 --> 21:24.280
Why does he want to see me?

21:27.410 --> 21:29.320
Should I prepare something for him?

21:29.320 --> 21:30.950
No need. He is a nice person.

21:34.180 --> 21:35.980
I heard him yelling you just now.

21:36.030 --> 21:37.270
Pup.

21:39.400 --> 21:41.320
Just think of it as a nickname.

21:42.880 --> 21:43.610
Don't laugh.

21:45.080 --> 21:45.630
Okay.

21:45.650 --> 21:46.780
I'll stop laughing.

21:47.710 --> 21:49.160
I'm going to change clothes.

21:49.160 --> 21:50.160
You should go too.

21:51.090 --> 21:52.020
Pup.

22:22.090 --> 22:22.700
Hansheng.

22:25.190 --> 22:26.920
I'll wash up and be ready soon.

22:27.750 --> 22:28.510
No rush.

22:56.860 --> 22:57.470
You're back.

22:57.470 --> 22:58.120
Dan.

22:58.800 --> 23:00.270
Chief Tan is waiting for you
in his office.

23:00.270 --> 23:01.230
Professor Jiang,

23:01.230 --> 23:02.220
Director Wang is in the reception room.

23:02.220 --> 23:03.350
I'll take you there.

23:04.710 --> 23:05.510
See you later.

23:09.920 --> 23:10.580
Reporting.

23:10.670 --> 23:11.160
Come in.

23:12.740 --> 23:13.220
Sir.

23:13.620 --> 23:14.680
Where is everyone?

23:15.450 --> 23:16.650
Do you think they are all like you,

23:16.650 --> 23:17.720
idling at home?

23:17.920 --> 23:19.120
They're busy as hell.

23:19.920 --> 23:21.250
I have a new case for you.

23:21.650 --> 23:23.230
Did we get a new lead on the 8.17 case?

23:23.230 --> 23:24.830
All you know is the 8.17 case.

23:25.030 --> 23:26.880
A homicide has occurred

23:26.990 --> 23:28.830
in Lishui Residential Area,
Lanjing Street.

23:28.830 --> 23:31.480
Based on the initial investigation
of the crime scene,

23:31.480 --> 23:32.660
it bears a strong resemblance

23:32.660 --> 23:34.360
to the two cases in Ningyuan and New Port

23:34.360 --> 23:35.490
earlier this month.

23:35.850 --> 23:37.240
You should go check out the crime scene.

23:37.240 --> 23:38.700
Is it a serial murder case?

23:38.840 --> 23:39.950
It's very likely.

23:40.670 --> 23:42.270
Director Wang Pengze is here

23:42.360 --> 23:43.510
for this case too.

23:44.030 --> 23:44.710
By the way,

23:45.590 --> 23:46.440
he personally

23:46.460 --> 23:48.220
requested you by name

23:48.250 --> 23:50.380
to participate in the investigation.

23:53.270 --> 23:54.230
Why me?

23:54.360 --> 23:55.320
How would I know?

23:55.930 --> 23:57.190
You'll have to ask him.

24:00.230 --> 24:02.290
Is there something you are afraid of?

24:03.080 --> 24:04.430
Hurry up and go.

24:08.370 --> 24:10.990
[Reception Room]

24:58.510 --> 24:59.790
Look who it is.

25:01.330 --> 25:04.010
It's the famous Professor Jiang.

25:05.160 --> 25:06.760
I've heard so much about you.

25:07.270 --> 25:08.840
If there's nothing important,

25:08.840 --> 25:10.640
you can just go back to sleeping.

25:11.450 --> 25:13.580
Just seeing you makes me angry
and gives me a headache.

25:13.580 --> 25:15.040
How am I supposed to sleep?

25:15.190 --> 25:16.400
You were snoring.

25:16.990 --> 25:18.320
Isn't it because of you?

25:18.510 --> 25:20.610
I told you to stay low in Haizhou

25:20.630 --> 25:22.150
and live a quiet life.

25:23.050 --> 25:24.460
But you had to do the opposite.

25:24.460 --> 25:26.920
You're almost a star now
in the police force.

25:29.880 --> 25:30.470
Sir.

25:31.600 --> 25:33.200
I'd love to live a quiet life.

25:34.070 --> 25:35.360
But they won't let me.

25:40.860 --> 25:43.550
[Two days ago]

25:50.640 --> 25:51.320
Sir.

25:52.920 --> 25:53.750
Pocket watch.

25:57.380 --> 25:58.780
They put the pocket watch

25:59.430 --> 26:01.230
next to Zhou Chuan's tombstone.

26:24.730 --> 26:25.590
Director Wang.

26:25.920 --> 26:26.640
Hello.

26:26.840 --> 26:29.110
I'm Zhou Jin, an investigator

26:29.230 --> 26:31.030
from the CIB of Nancheng Branch.

26:31.950 --> 26:32.990
Zhou.

26:35.560 --> 26:36.890
Hansheng is my student.

26:37.160 --> 26:38.490
So that makes us family.

26:38.980 --> 26:40.370
He always talks about you.

26:40.370 --> 26:41.840
I finally get to meet you today.

26:41.840 --> 26:43.440
You're just like I imagined.

26:43.510 --> 26:44.320
Excellent.

26:44.360 --> 26:45.810
Very good.

26:46.640 --> 26:47.060
Director Wang.

26:47.060 --> 26:49.560
Hansheng and I should have been the ones
to visit you.

26:49.560 --> 26:50.690
I'm just an old man.

26:51.080 --> 26:52.210
What's there to see?

26:53.200 --> 26:54.780
I used to work in criminal investigation.

26:54.780 --> 26:57.040
I know how hard you are
on the front lines.

26:57.320 --> 26:59.110
Visiting or not isn't important.

26:59.110 --> 27:00.330
The important thing is

27:00.330 --> 27:01.800
you need to care for him more

27:01.800 --> 27:03.080
and be a bit more patient

27:03.080 --> 27:04.320
with this silly boy.

27:08.920 --> 27:11.520
Captain Tan has briefed you on the case,
right?

27:11.970 --> 27:13.630
He filled me in on everything.

27:14.240 --> 27:15.810
This is a major case.

27:16.240 --> 27:17.570
I came to Haizhou alone.

27:17.760 --> 27:19.180
I need someone from your team

27:19.180 --> 27:20.220
to work with me.

27:20.640 --> 27:22.090
I've thought it over,

27:23.600 --> 27:25.270
and I think you're the right person.

27:25.270 --> 27:27.750
Also, Hansheng, as my student,

27:28.200 --> 27:30.660
will participate in the investigation too.

27:31.430 --> 27:32.140
Sir,

27:32.440 --> 27:33.410
what kind of case

27:33.570 --> 27:35.500
would bring you to the front lines?

27:36.190 --> 27:38.450
You'll know once you see the crime scene.

27:38.580 --> 27:39.650
I came here at 8 this morning.

27:39.650 --> 27:40.250
At 8.

27:40.250 --> 27:41.930
Have you delivered packages to her before?

27:41.930 --> 27:42.970
Yes, I have.

27:43.250 --> 27:45.060
Do you know the homeowner's name?

27:45.060 --> 27:46.100
No, I don't.

27:46.100 --> 27:46.890
Jin,

27:47.060 --> 27:48.190
you're back on duty?

27:49.620 --> 27:50.780
Excuse me, everyone. Coming through.

27:50.780 --> 27:52.310
Excuse me, coming through.

27:53.450 --> 27:54.520
Has the body been taken away?

27:54.520 --> 27:56.450
Not yet. Dr. Lin is still upstairs.

27:56.710 --> 27:58.780
Right on time, Director Wang. We're ready.

27:58.780 --> 28:00.670
Please head up to the second floor
and take a look.

28:00.670 --> 28:01.060
Okay.

28:01.340 --> 28:02.170
Let's go upstairs.

28:02.170 --> 28:03.320
Yes, this way.

28:33.550 --> 28:34.200
Lin.

28:34.460 --> 28:35.670
Suicide or homicide?

28:35.830 --> 28:36.630
Homicide.

28:43.620 --> 28:46.280
It has a strong emotional
and ritualistic tone.

28:46.590 --> 28:47.740
It's quite creepy.

29:16.360 --> 29:17.050
Have you taken pictures?

29:17.050 --> 29:17.640
Yes.

29:42.150 --> 29:44.680
If there's only
a single incision on the wrist

29:44.870 --> 29:47.400
with no other
superficial hesitation marks,

29:47.430 --> 29:48.490
it means the killer

29:48.500 --> 29:50.260
only made one cut.

29:51.170 --> 29:53.970
But there's no significant bloodstain
by the bed.

29:55.090 --> 29:57.090
This isn't the primary crime scene.

29:58.500 --> 29:59.480
It's the bathroom, right?

29:59.480 --> 29:59.960
Yes.

31:15.340 --> 31:17.670
No.

31:23.670 --> 31:24.280
No.

31:26.020 --> 31:26.540
No.

31:26.910 --> 31:27.590
Please.

31:28.230 --> 31:29.380
I'm begging.

31:29.910 --> 31:30.430
No.

31:30.500 --> 31:30.910
No.

31:33.750 --> 31:34.300
No.

31:35.860 --> 31:36.700
No!

32:06.890 --> 32:07.530
Hansheng.

32:17.030 --> 32:17.470
Jin.

32:21.640 --> 32:23.620
We've pretty much got all the information.

32:23.620 --> 32:24.880
The victim's name is Zhao Xiaoyu.

32:24.880 --> 32:26.610
She's 27 years old. Unmarried.

32:26.750 --> 32:28.360
Her parents bought this apartment for her,

32:28.360 --> 32:29.860
and she usually lived here alone.

32:29.860 --> 32:31.060
When was it reported?

32:31.510 --> 32:32.470
This morning.

32:32.670 --> 32:34.860
The person who reported it
is the delivery guy downstairs.

32:34.860 --> 32:35.820
Before Zhao Xiaoyu died,

32:35.820 --> 32:37.420
she ordered flowers online.

32:37.540 --> 32:38.190
Every Monday,

32:38.190 --> 32:40.190
a delivery guy would deliver them
to her door.

32:40.190 --> 32:41.710
Today, when the delivery guy arrived,

32:41.710 --> 32:42.910
he noticed the door was unlocked.

32:42.910 --> 32:44.510
He intended to come in just to remind her,

32:44.510 --> 32:45.750
but as soon as he stepped inside,

32:45.750 --> 32:46.780
he noticed a strange smell.

32:46.780 --> 32:48.110
So he called the police.

32:48.790 --> 32:50.050
We're heading off now.

32:50.430 --> 32:51.030
Take care.

32:57.990 --> 32:59.230
Have the family been notified?

32:59.230 --> 32:59.910
Yes.

33:00.140 --> 33:01.140
Her parents are out of town.

33:01.140 --> 33:03.070
They won't be here until tomorrow.

33:04.190 --> 33:05.780
Director Wang compared the scenes.

33:05.780 --> 33:06.550
He said

33:06.780 --> 33:09.620
it seems like the same killer
as in Ningyuan and New Port.

33:09.620 --> 33:10.340
I heard.

33:10.950 --> 33:12.150
A serial murder case.

33:12.380 --> 33:14.580
The smell of disinfectant is so strong.

33:14.580 --> 33:15.980
And the scene is so clean.

33:16.100 --> 33:17.000
The killer really

33:17.000 --> 33:19.060
cleaned up the scene very carefully.

33:19.300 --> 33:20.700
The MO is highly skilled.

33:20.990 --> 33:22.340
The target is very clear.

33:22.340 --> 33:23.940
And it's a mobile operation.

33:24.540 --> 33:27.510
This has completely stepped
outside the psychological safety zone.

33:27.510 --> 33:28.620
The killer is very dangerous.

33:28.620 --> 33:30.240
We must catch him as soon as possible.

33:30.240 --> 33:31.620
In terms of criminal features,

33:31.620 --> 33:32.820
these three cases

33:33.030 --> 33:34.620
are very similar

33:34.620 --> 33:35.990
to the Huaiguang serial murder case.

33:35.990 --> 33:37.150
The signature elements such as

33:37.150 --> 33:38.100
women in red dresses,

33:38.100 --> 33:38.710
roses,

33:38.860 --> 33:39.390
and bows,

33:40.540 --> 33:42.470
as well as his handling of the scenes,

33:42.470 --> 33:43.930
the posture of the bodies,

33:43.950 --> 33:45.880
and the fatal wounds on the wrists.

33:47.100 --> 33:48.100
They are the same.

33:49.910 --> 33:50.430
But...

33:50.670 --> 33:51.750
But five years ago,

33:52.270 --> 33:54.670
the killer of the Huaiguang serial murders

33:54.800 --> 33:56.450
was already shot dead by you!

33:59.230 --> 34:00.030
Not only that.

34:01.540 --> 34:03.000
It's not exactly the same.

34:03.920 --> 34:04.850
What do you mean?

34:05.510 --> 34:06.060
The bows.

34:07.040 --> 34:08.540
Although they are all bows,

34:08.540 --> 34:10.040
they're tied in different ways.

34:10.040 --> 34:12.570
Especially this one.
It's a three-layer bow.

34:12.719 --> 34:14.250
It's very difficult to tie.

34:14.370 --> 34:16.570
But he tied it perfectly, full and neat.

34:19.020 --> 34:19.719
This kind of bow

34:19.719 --> 34:22.280
is only used

34:22.389 --> 34:24.050
when giving a gift to someone.

34:28.429 --> 34:30.330
Could this be his gift to Qi Yan?

34:32.540 --> 34:34.719
The details of Qi Yan's cases

34:35.659 --> 34:37.179
are not fully disclosed.

34:37.469 --> 34:38.290
How could he

34:38.310 --> 34:38.909
imitate it

34:38.989 --> 34:40.060
to this extent?

34:41.510 --> 34:42.510
It's impossible.

34:43.790 --> 34:45.320
Do you think he knows Qi Yan?

34:47.659 --> 34:48.690
Rather than saying

34:48.690 --> 34:49.780
he knows Qi Yan,

34:50.469 --> 34:51.429
it's more like

34:51.460 --> 34:52.920
he's taking Qi Yan's place

34:52.929 --> 34:55.060
and coming back to take revenge on you.

34:57.160 --> 34:57.910
Isn't it?

35:00.830 --> 35:01.540
This case,

35:02.580 --> 35:04.240
and the pocket watch you lost.

35:05.870 --> 35:07.400
He's sending you a message.

35:09.540 --> 35:10.400
One more thing.

35:11.400 --> 35:13.130
He knows I'm afraid of needles.

35:30.690 --> 35:32.890
This is his gift to you.

35:51.430 --> 35:52.040
Wei.

35:53.180 --> 35:53.700
Jin,

35:54.260 --> 35:55.260
where are you now?

35:55.620 --> 35:57.080
I'm at the crime scene now.

35:57.510 --> 35:59.040
Is there anyone around you?

35:59.430 --> 36:00.990
I'm alone now. Why?

36:01.560 --> 36:02.990
Find a place with no one around.

36:02.990 --> 36:03.790
Just you.

36:03.790 --> 36:05.190
Don't bring anyone else.

36:05.790 --> 36:06.920
I am alone right now.

36:07.060 --> 36:08.190
Go ahead and tell me.

36:08.390 --> 36:09.120
Are you sure?

36:09.910 --> 36:11.470
What exactly happened, Wei?

36:11.470 --> 36:13.330
You're making me really nervous.

36:13.510 --> 36:15.220
The informant you asked me to look into,

36:15.220 --> 36:16.750
the one helping Yao Weihai,

36:17.220 --> 36:18.470
I found out his name.

36:20.060 --> 36:21.140
It's your husband.

36:21.390 --> 36:22.320
Jiang Hansheng.

36:31.430 --> 36:32.540
Are you sure?

36:33.390 --> 36:35.100
If you want to know more,

36:35.540 --> 36:37.940
I suggest you ask Jiang Hansheng directly.

36:38.260 --> 36:39.180
Has he never

36:39.210 --> 36:40.690
told you about this?

36:41.700 --> 36:42.910
He never said a word.

36:44.320 --> 36:45.050
Jin,

36:45.870 --> 36:47.030
you might want to take a good look

36:47.030 --> 36:48.030
at your marriage.

36:49.100 --> 36:50.830
I'm not like Bin.

36:50.830 --> 36:52.390
I don't think Jiang Cheng

36:52.390 --> 36:54.030
is the only one you should marry.

36:54.030 --> 36:54.700
But I still feel

36:54.700 --> 36:57.300
Jiang Hansheng's appearance
is very strange.

36:57.720 --> 36:59.220
Are you sure that blind date

36:59.220 --> 37:01.820
was the first time you met him
since childhood?

37:04.510 --> 37:05.510
Why do you ask?

37:05.910 --> 37:08.640
I asked around about Jiang Hansheng
in the Provincial Bureau.

37:08.640 --> 37:09.700
Opinions about him

37:09.700 --> 37:10.990
are sharply divided.

37:11.350 --> 37:12.470
Those who like him

37:12.910 --> 37:14.180
praise his professional skills.

37:14.180 --> 37:15.100
Those who don't

37:15.100 --> 37:16.530
describe him as paranoid, cold,

37:16.530 --> 37:18.470
and completely lacking in human warmth.

37:18.470 --> 37:20.270
But one thing everyone agrees on

37:20.350 --> 37:21.580
is that his obsession with cases

37:21.580 --> 37:22.740
and his pursuit of details

37:22.740 --> 37:24.940
are far beyond normal police officers.

37:25.060 --> 37:26.430
He's especially addicted

37:26.430 --> 37:28.030
to murders and bloody cases.

37:28.620 --> 37:29.700
In my opinion,

37:30.060 --> 37:31.470
he is a freak.

37:32.220 --> 37:33.310
Jin,

37:33.830 --> 37:35.890
you two have been married for a while.

37:36.260 --> 37:37.390
Don't you feel it?

37:41.870 --> 37:42.350
Jin.

37:43.470 --> 37:44.330
I'm listening.

37:45.100 --> 37:47.760
Is Jiang Hansheng with you
because he loves you,

37:47.790 --> 37:49.450
or does he have other motives?

37:50.180 --> 37:52.180
Does he see you as a subject to study,

37:52.290 --> 37:54.620
as an entry point into an unsolved case,

37:55.310 --> 37:56.970
or is there some other reason?

37:58.700 --> 37:59.500
Jin,

38:00.330 --> 38:02.290
I advise you to be more careful.

38:03.030 --> 38:04.130
Don't be naive.

38:05.260 --> 38:07.190
Don't love the wrong person again.

38:07.580 --> 38:08.180
Zhou Jin.

38:08.700 --> 38:10.070
You have no experience

38:10.100 --> 38:12.220
confronting the people
behind the 8.17 Case.

38:12.220 --> 38:13.350
Their past actions

38:13.580 --> 38:16.310
prove they have strong
provocative tendencies.

38:16.510 --> 38:17.790
When provocation fails,

38:17.790 --> 38:18.870
revenge follows.

38:20.180 --> 38:22.510
I used to carry out some special missions.

38:22.980 --> 38:24.110
They left me on edge.

38:26.910 --> 38:27.430
Hello?

38:28.870 --> 38:29.390
Jin,

38:29.660 --> 38:31.060
are you still listening?

38:32.780 --> 38:34.100
I got it, Wei.

38:34.180 --> 38:35.100
Thank you.

38:35.450 --> 38:36.510
I'm busy right now.

38:36.510 --> 38:37.280
I gotta go.

38:53.470 --> 38:54.910
The day you called

38:54.910 --> 38:57.170
and told me you'd lost that pocket watch,

38:57.280 --> 38:59.280
I knew this case wasn't simple.

38:59.740 --> 39:01.390
The killing isn't the point.

39:01.390 --> 39:02.470
His main purpose

39:03.220 --> 39:04.580
is to send you a message.

39:04.660 --> 39:05.910
He's telling you

39:06.870 --> 39:08.100
he's coming for you.

39:16.870 --> 39:18.660
Zhou, come here.

39:24.910 --> 39:26.170
Did you find anything?

39:26.430 --> 39:27.870
The scene investigation is complete.

39:27.870 --> 39:29.390
We'll further

39:29.390 --> 39:31.390
investigate the victim's social circle

39:31.390 --> 39:33.030
and check the security cameras

39:33.030 --> 39:35.450
to confirm the killer's whereabouts
as soon as possible.

39:35.450 --> 39:36.130
Mr. Wang.

39:36.220 --> 39:38.750
Is there anything else
you think we should do?

39:39.100 --> 39:41.100
The routine investigation is done.

39:41.260 --> 39:42.720
And you've seen the scene.

39:42.990 --> 39:44.030
Do you think there might be

39:44.030 --> 39:45.630
any other angles to explore?

39:47.180 --> 39:49.260
The killer is very skilled.

39:49.310 --> 39:50.770
He's clearly not a rookie.

39:50.910 --> 39:52.620
Generally, in serial murder cases,

39:52.620 --> 39:53.580
we focus heavily on

39:53.580 --> 39:55.040
the killer's first crime.

39:55.100 --> 39:56.470
Because during the first crime,

39:56.470 --> 39:57.580
the methods aren't as mature.

39:57.580 --> 39:59.220
It's easy to leave flaws,

39:59.220 --> 40:00.480
along with more clues.

40:00.660 --> 40:02.870
Plus, the urge to kill is usually stronger
in the first crime,

40:02.870 --> 40:04.100
making it easier to figure out

40:04.100 --> 40:05.300
the killer's motive.

40:10.230 --> 40:11.230
Did you hear that?

40:11.660 --> 40:13.140
She answers when asked.

40:15.620 --> 40:16.700
Unlike someone,

40:16.950 --> 40:18.410
who's a total closed book.

40:18.910 --> 40:20.310
Every time I take him to a crime scene,

40:20.310 --> 40:21.440
I ask ten questions,

40:21.510 --> 40:23.710
and getting one answer is already a win.

40:24.700 --> 40:25.900
I need to think.

40:26.390 --> 40:27.180
Yeah, right.

40:27.220 --> 40:29.140
Only you can think,
and the rest of us can't?

40:29.140 --> 40:29.870
Take me back.

40:30.430 --> 40:30.830
Okay.

40:50.150 --> 40:50.800
Mr. Wang.

40:50.830 --> 40:52.030
Once the investigation results are out,

40:52.030 --> 40:53.540
I'll send them to you immediately.

40:53.540 --> 40:53.990
Okay.

40:55.090 --> 40:55.820
I'm going in.

41:00.930 --> 41:03.330
Are you heading back
to the precinct later?

41:05.580 --> 41:07.060
Since it's a serial murder case,

41:07.060 --> 41:08.140
there should be a lot of related cases

41:08.140 --> 41:09.270
I need to go through.

41:13.990 --> 41:14.540
Zhou Jin.

41:15.110 --> 41:16.240
Is something wrong?

41:20.310 --> 41:21.310
What is it?

41:28.990 --> 41:30.050
Did I do something?

41:37.980 --> 41:38.840
Are you hungry?

41:41.960 --> 41:42.560
No.

41:43.310 --> 41:44.030
I'm hungry.

41:45.540 --> 41:46.800
What do you want to eat?

41:46.860 --> 41:47.740
Instant noodles.

41:47.740 --> 41:48.300
And beer.

41:50.750 --> 41:52.280
No drinking while on a case.

41:52.310 --> 41:53.970
You asked what I wanted to eat.

41:56.020 --> 41:57.310
Let's grab a bite together.

41:57.310 --> 41:59.370
I actually have something to ask you.

41:59.660 --> 42:00.390
Get in.

42:14.990 --> 42:16.510
Fei. Fei.

42:19.430 --> 42:20.210
He's so handsome.

42:20.210 --> 42:21.030
Really handsome.

42:21.030 --> 42:22.030
You should ask him for his WeChat.

42:22.030 --> 42:22.660
You go.

42:22.660 --> 42:23.870
You go first.

42:25.240 --> 42:26.700
I think that's his girlfriend.

42:26.700 --> 42:27.960
Maybe we should leave.

43:03.730 --> 43:04.930
Let's just have beer.

43:05.460 --> 43:06.660
Let's play a game.
